
# Instruccions - Backend Enviroment

Run the following commands 
>Use *py* in windows or *python* in linux

```bash
py -m venv getXerpa
source getXerpa/scripts/activate
pip install djangorestframework
pip install drf-nested-routers
python -m pip install django-cors-headers
cd backend
py manage.py runserver
```

# Endpoints

>Categories

* GET: http://localhost:8000/api/category/
* GET: http://localhost:8000/api/category/:id/
* POST: http://localhost:8000/api/category/
* PUT: http://localhost:8000/api/category/:id/
* PATCH: http://localhost:8000/api/category/:id/
* DELETE: http://localhost:8000/api/category/:id/

* GET: http://localhost:8000/api/category/limit_exceeded?exceeded
- exceeded = 1: return the categories that exceeded the limit
- exceeded = 0: return the categories that did not exceed the limit
- send nothing: return both


>Transactions

* GET: http://localhost:8000/api/transaction/
* GET: http://localhost:8000/api/transaction/:id/
* POST: http://localhost:8000/api/transaction/
* PUT: http://localhost:8000/api/transaction/:id/
* PATCH: http://localhost:8000/api/transaction/:id/
* DELETE: http://localhost:8000/api/transaction/:id/


# Instruccions - Forntend Enviroment

Run the following commands 

```bash
npm i -g @angular/cli
cd frontend
npm i
npm start
```